ander the Great |publisher=Haus |isbn=978-1-904341-56-7 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Connerney |first=R. D. |year=2009 |title=The upside-down tree: India's changing culture |url=https://books.google.com/?id=4WadcncjsRUC |publisher=Algora |isbn=978-0-87586-649-9 |ref=harv |page=214}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Curtis |first1=J. |last2=Tallis |first2=N |last3=Andre-Salvini |first3=B |year=2005 |title=Forgotten empire: the world of ancient Persia |page=154 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kJnaKu9DdNEC |publisher=University of California Press |isbn=978-0-520-24731-4 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Dahmen |first=Karsten |year=2007 |title=The Legend of Alexander the Great on Greek and Roman Coins |publisher=Taylor & Francis |isbn=978-0-415-39451-2 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Danforth |first=Loring M. |year=1997 |title=The Macedonian Conflict: Ethnic Nationalism in a Transnational World |publisher=Princeton University Press |isbn=978-0-691-04356-2 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Dillon |first=John M. |year=2004 |title=Morality and custom in ancient Greece |publisher=Indiana University Press |isbn=978-0-253-34526-4 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Durant |first=Will |authorlink=Will Durant |year=1966 |title=The Story of Civilization: The Life of Greece |publisher=Simon & Schuster |isbn=978-0-671-41800-7 |ref=harv |url=https://archive.org/details/lifeofgreece02dura }}\n* {{cite book |first=Patrick Leigh |last=Fermor |year=2006 |title=Mani: Travels in the Southern Peloponnese |url=https://books.google.com/?id=8V5QBkD7IIYC |publisher=[[New York Book Review]] |isbn=978-1-59017-188-2 |ref=harv |page=358}}\n* {{cite book |last=Fischer |first=MMJ |year=2004 |title=Mute dreams, blind owls, and dispersed knowledges: Persian poesis in the transnational circuitry |page=66 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=KibBH6cI8BgC |publisher=Duke University Press |isbn=978-0-8223-3298-5 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Foreman |first=Laura |year=2004 |title=Alexander the conqueror: th